      <title><![CDATA[ Annette Verschuren - From a small-town dairy farmer to a global change-maker]]></title>
      <itunes:title><![CDATA[ Annette Verschuren - From a small-town dairy farmer to a global change-maker]]></itunes:title>
      <description><![CDATA[From a small-town dairy farmer to a global change-maker, Annette Verschuren has built a career on taking risks, being unapologetically brazen, and <strong>prioritizing purpose with profits.</strong>Co-founder of the craft chain, Michaels Canada, former CEO of Home Depot Canada and Asia, Co-Founder of trailblazing clean-tech firm, NRStor, best-selling author and, now, podcaster, Annette has a clear mission to inspire budding leaders to look within, harness their strengths and bet on themselves. Tune in to hear her incredible journey!]]></description>
